  "instructions": [
    "Heat coconut oil to 375°F (190°C) in a deep frying pan.",
    "Rinse the shiso leaves and pat them dry with a paper towel.",
    "In a blender, blend the coconut milk, scotch bonnet peppers, garlic cloves, onion, and salt.",
    "Add the almond flour to the blender and blend until smooth.",
    "Cut the chicken breast into small pieces and dredge them in the almond flour mixture.",
    "Add the chicken pieces to the hot oil and fry until golden brown.",
    "Add the shiso leaves to the oil and fry for 1-2 minutes or until they start to wilt.",
    "Drain the agemono on paper towels and serve hot."
  ],
